==步骤========
一：PackageTool开发环境部署
二：被打包项目的Ios开发环境部署
三：被打包项目的Android开发环境部署

==软件安装========
一：PackageTool开发环境部署
1.1 软件：idk:https://login.oracle.com/mysso/signon.jsp JDK
       IDEA:http://www.jetbrains.com/idea/#chooseYourEdition
       Android studio:http://www.androiddevtools.cn/
       maven:https://maven.apache.org/download.cgi .tar.gz
       grade:https://gradle.org/releases complete
       tomcat:http://tomcat.apache.org/download-90.cgi  zip
       cornerstone：http://www.pc6.com/mac/111958.html
       GitHub:https://git-scm.com/downloads/
       ant:http://ant.apache.org/bindownload.cgi  zip
       mysql:https://dev.mysql.com/downloads/
       MySQL Community Server+MySQL Workbench
       http://www.cnblogs.com/macro-cheng/archive/2011/10/25/mysql-001.html
       MYSQL命令无法识别—建立软链接
       sudo ln -s /usr/local/mysql-5.7.17-macos10.12-x86_64/bin/mysql /usr/local/bin
       2017-03-16T03:12:01.561053Z 1 [Note] A temporary password is generated for root@localhost: 1Bf+eQZCjM0=
       mysql -uroot -p
       1Bf+eQZCjM0=
       alter user 'root'@'localhost' identified by 'root';
       flush privileges;
       exit;
       mysql -uroot -p
       create database packagetool;
       use packagetool
       source /Volumes/HHD/IDEAworkspace/packagetools/packagetool.sql
1.2 IntelliJ:
1.2.1 下载源代码，用导入maven工程的方式打开工程文件后，在configurations中增加Tomact server, 在deployment中增加war exploded
1.2.2 修改数据库, 修改文件ApplicationContext.xml中的数据源
            <value>jdbc:mysql://localhost:3306/packagetool?useUnicode=true&amp;characterEncoding=UTF-8</value>
1.3 Mysql: 执行指令更换密码mysqladmin -u root -p password root 输入初始密码，完成
1.4 Navicat: 创建数据库packagetook, 执行packagetool.sql创建表和相关数据
1.6 ext包：提供的ext包中的内容拷贝到环境变量JAVA_HOME目录下的jre/lib与lib目录下
1.7 Tomecat配置
1.7.1 制作app.pem和app.keystore(自行baidu)
1.7.2 app.pem作为客户端下载的证书放置在webapps/downipa/ca中
1.7.3 app.keystore放置在apache-tomcat-7.0.69/conf/下
1.7.4 在tomcat中的server.xml配置app.keystore
<Connector port="8443" protocol="org.apache.coyote.http11.Http11Protocol" maxThreads="150" SSLEnabled="true" scheme="https" secure="true" keystoreFile="xxx/apache-tomcat-7.0.69/conf/app.keystore" keystorePass="111111" clientAuth="false" sslProtocol="TLS" />
1.7.5 配置路径映射, 在tomcat中的server.xml配置
在 <Host name="localhost" appBase="webapps" unpackWARs="true" autoDeploy="true"> 的下一行配置 
<Context path="" docBase="../webapps/packagetool" debug="0" reloadable="false"/> <Context path="down" docBase="../webapps/downipa"/>

二：被打包项目的Ios开发环境部署
2.1 软件：Xcode, ...
2.2 xcode-preferences-Locations-Derived Data 选择Relative，填写build（目的是为了指定生成的包的存放位置）
如直接写build则代表当前目录下的build文件夹

三：被打包项目的Android开发环境部署
3.1 软件：Android Studio, Gradle, Android SDK, ...

==环境变量========
$ vim ~/.bash_profile
export JAVA_HOME=/Library/Java/JavaVirtualMachines/jdk1.8.0_111.jdk/Contents/Home
export JRE_HOME=/Library/Java/JavaVirtualMachines/jdk1.8.0_111.jdk/Contents/Home/jre
export M2_HOME=/Volumes/HHD/development/apache-maven-3.3.9
#export TOMCAT_HOME=/Users/catty/Documents/dev/apache-tomcat-8.5.12
export TOMCAT_HOME=/Volumes/HHD/development/apache-tomcat-8.5.12
#export GRADLE_HOME=/Volumes/HHD/development/gradle-3.0
export GRADLE_HOME=/Users/catty/Documents/dev/gradle-3.0
export ANT_HOME=/Volumes/HHD/development/apache-ant-1.10.1
export ANDROID_HOME=/Volumes/HHD/development/sdk
export JENKINS_HOME=/Volumes/HHD/development/apache-tomcat-8.5.12/webapps
export PATH=$PATH:${JENKINS_HOME}:${GRADLE_HOME}/bin:${JAVA_HOME}/bin:${JAVA_HOME}/lib/Tools.jar:${JRE_HOME}/bin:${TOMCAT_HOME}/bin:${ANDROID_HOME}/platform-tools:${ANDROID_HOME}/tools:${M2_HOME}/bin:${ANT_HOME}/bin
#export PATH=/opt/subversion/bin:$PATH
export PATH=/usr/local/bin:/usr/bin:/bin:/usr/sbin:/sbin:$PATH
==troubleshooting========
1. 下载ios包失败：某台服务器tomacat7与jdk8 https(Ios下载包需要用https)不通，tomcat9与jdk8不通，tomcat7与jdk7，能够联通https，所以建议使用tomcat7与jdk7版本来部署
2. Android编译时加载com.android.tools.build:gradle:x.x.x失败，重新安装JDK并重启电脑
3. PackageTool编译时svn相关库函数识别失败，ext中增加相关库函数移除，重启电脑，移入，再重启电脑